---
// AboutTeaser.astro
---
<section class="section about-teaser">
  <div class="container split-layout">
    <div class="content animate-fade-in">
      <span class="badge">WELCOME TO AAYRONIX HUB</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Driving Real Impact Through <span class="text-gradient">Talent & Technology</span></h2>
      <p class="lead-text">With over 30 years of combined experience, our founders lead AAYRONIX HUB in delivering real impact through talent and technology.</p>
      <p>We help businesses scale, innovate, and stay ahead—because we understand the pulse and needs of today’s organisations. Our hallmark is hassle-free talent delivery, building scalable teams, and accelerating business growth.</p>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-6);">Learn More About Us</a>
    </div>
    <div class="visual">
      <div class="image-container animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <img src="/corporate_about.png?v=987" alt="AAYRONIX HUB Professional Corporate Team" />
      </div>
      <div class="stats-container">
        <div class="stat-card glass">
          <h3 class="counter-up" data-target="30" data-suffix="+">0+</h3>
          <p>Years Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card glass">
          <h3>Global</h3>
          <p>Talent Network</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .content p {
    text-align: justify;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

  .visual {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .visual::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    filter: blur(100px);
    opacity: 0.2;
    z-index: -1;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .stat-card {
    flex: 1;
    padding: var(--spacing-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .stat-card h3 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
  }

  .stat-card p {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .image-container {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .image-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .stats-container {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-6);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .split-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .stats-container {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
